Abdul Rashid Salim Salman Khan is the most well-known Indian actor, singer, film producer, painter, and television personality who work mostly in Hindi cinema. He is well-known for his services to Hindi cinema over the last 30 years, appearing in over 80 films.

He has received many awards for his work in Bollywood, including Filmfare Awards, National Film Awards, Star Screen Awards, Zee Cine Awards and others.

Without question, he is one of India's highest-paid performers. With a net worth of $37.7 million, he was named to Fobes' 2018 Top-Paid 100 Celebrity Entertainers List.